    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时尚潜行动作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以敏捷的冲刺掠过视线死角，用优雅的姿态探索这个世界。你的探索方式，将决定少年的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/19284694d51d87cb3596ae58261696a4.poster.avif?t=1771349024\" width=638 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/19284694d51d87cb3596ae58261696a4.webm?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/19284694d51d87cb3596ae58261696a4.mp4?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐藏在地下世界的谜团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集散落在世界各处的滤镜，达什便会不断成长。随着力量的积累，那些过去只能转身逃避的敌人，也不再令人恐惧。可探索的疆域随之扩展，而探索本身，又将引出更多未知的谜团。三大区域的探索顺序，将决定截然不同的故事走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/1a13285cb9c521737ddff814b865735c.poster.avif?t=1771349024\" width=632 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/1a13285cb9c521737ddff814b865735c.webm?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/1a13285cb9c521737ddff814b865735c.mp4?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>文明崩溃后脆弱而美丽的街景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它的衰落并不轰烈。地下世界在静谧与安宁中缓缓消逝。荒废的车站、废弃的矿坑、深红的宗教之城……这脆弱的景象，如今只剩你来见证。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/d9220054e79bcfa798f06eb01cc8dfb7.poster.avif?t=1771349024\" width=642 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/d9220054e79bcfa798f06eb01cc8dfb7.webm?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/d9220054e79bcfa798f06eb01cc8dfb7.mp4?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>曾经从世界消逝之物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在毁灭的世界中，少年邂逅了被病痛束缚的少女。为了将她从封闭的房间中解放，他踏入了被机械占据的黑暗深处。是否选择相信她的引领，全凭你自己决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/3284410f0f0627fa079a60d77e6b1519.poster.avif?t=1771349024\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/3284410f0f0627fa079a60d77e6b1519.webm?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/3284410f0f0627fa079a60d77e6b1519.mp4?t=1771349024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品已被文化厅与CESA共同设立的创作者培养计划“TGCA”选中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039960/extras/565fadd7bfad15e2da1d3bac4461c8c9.avif?t=1771349024\" width=839 height=311 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时间　: 10小时</p>",
